{"tid":2369411,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"群星雲集典禮 Lady Gaga獻唱美國國歌","createTime":"2021-01-17T06:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T07:19:06.000Z","uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a900747cc28a376f5f945a4a27eb865b80bc2a59","tid":2369411,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2850000/2853989/150121_ceremony_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2850000%2F2853989%2F150121_ceremony_1024.jpg&h=30b90a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拜登將於下周三（20日）舉行美國總統就職典禮，外界關注拜登就職典禮流程。拜登就職典禮主題為「美國團結」（America United），團隊更籌劃拜登就職典禮電視節目。多位美國明星將會出席慶祝拜登就職，而Lady Gaga更負責獻唱美國國歌。<br />\n<br />\n美媒CNN引述總統就職委員會官員指，團隊計劃製作拜登（Joe Biden）就職典禮特備節目取代傳統慶祝活動，料於當地下周三晚上8點半至10點播出。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，奧斯卡影帝湯漢斯（Tom Hanks）將會負責主持節目。而女歌手Lady Gaga在美國大選期間曾為拜登站台，她當晚會獻唱美國國歌。其他出席的明星包括珍妮花露柏絲（Jennifer Lopez）、搖滾巨星Jon Bon Jovi、前迪士尼童星兼女歌手洛瓦托（Demi Lovato）、知名男歌手Justin Timberlake及Ant Clemons。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國各界名人也出席拜登的就職典禮，以體現拜登「美國團結」的就職典禮主題。美國史上首位青年桂冠詩人戈曼（Amanda Gorman），將於典禮上朗誦詩文。而國際消防員聯會佐治亞州富爾頓縣（Fulton）分區主席霍爾（Andrea Hall）將會發表效忠誓詞，她也是該部門首位黑人女性消防隊長。<br />\n<br />\n拜登多年好友、喬治敦大學前校長奧多諾萬（Leo J. O'Donovan）會於典禮上讀禱文。而特拉華州威爾明頓的非洲衛理公會教堂牧師比曼（ Silvester Beaman）將負責作祝福。"},{"pid":"b22ec94295722efe1c5f8aa4777f9343f3079d3d","tid":2369411,"uid":24788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"唔夠黑wo"},{"pid":"54429dd3b276d10d579f6269e54582d607e50ee4","tid":2369411,"uid":200083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"臭閪gaga"},{"pid":"62dc9692d9dd612305d2b95a805b3446539fc0f8","tid":2369411,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"唱支那國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb510cc3133c9770339f19080297fba785c8b8a5","tid":2369411,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾左膠"},{"pid":"2822641ea8a3a897322af75a8a88921d57b35c1e","tid":2369411,"uid":335664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"哇！珍妮佛&middot;羅培茲！"},{"pid":"cf6a6c463b9f49634ea64aecb4a8e0209a48135f","tid":2369411,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:48:05.000Z","msg":"光明會"},{"pid":"9b41414b61a60233843e63638c7cfe0f13c6c69c","tid":2369411,"uid":223531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}